{"tid":798563,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"痾完屎，遇到靈異事件...","createTime":"2018-08-29T11:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T13:17:26.000Z","uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"69d62d8e3850b46d29bf3fd9f1c1b6412914b0f4","tid":798563,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:26:02.000Z","msg":"話說岩先急屎，就去痾，痾完，就去抹屎眼<br />\n喺我拎住張摺左3層既廁紙既時候，屎眼知道自己將要被卒，本能地收縮一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n怪事就黎啦，屎忽夾左一下之後，我feel到有舊軟軟地既野喺屎眼出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心中一諗到要用廁紙抹返舊屎出黎就覺得核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你咩仆街<br />\n但面對困難，只有勇敢地去解決，我一野就抹落去（隔住廁紙啦梗係）<br />\n<br />\n一抹完出黎望下張紙，咦？屎呢？我剩係見到紙上沾滿殘餘既屎汁，除此之外別無一物，但我再夾一下屎眼，仲係有舊野喺度喎....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是我再抹，都係屎汁黎，但我再夾一下屎眼，feel到舊屎已經冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成件事真係好不安，究竟係咪有野干預我腦神經，影響我屎眼既觸覺，令我誤以為有舊屎喺度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定係舊屎喺無意中被量子化左，因為我由頭到尾都有望到過一眼，我冇觀察佢，於是舊屎就喺一個存在同不存在之間既疊加態裏面？？而我屎眼一夾同廁紙一抹，就令e兩個可能情況塔縮至一個，而2次結果都唔同！<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚恐怖。。。"},{"pid":"3ed049961aa7f12d3171a7b8d22f3586ee145229","tid":798563,"uid":108912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:27:29.000Z","msg":"我睇咗乜撚嘢"},{"pid":"944f332064d091ecbb98cc954c566fe5813050e5","tid":798563,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe52ca800dcb374cc721970a02569ee2ed8227fc","tid":798563,"uid":142222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:40:10.000Z","msg":"潮唔起...有啲尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30ba3047d7ab88c8a8a10aabe7346583d6ba242","tid":798563,"uid":27743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:43:07.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"fe06a156f01affd35e4f48a80364bb9b1356ae62","tid":798563,"uid":172313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:44:12.000Z","msg":"kai子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0713dad2bf9be0474ec70d3a3c6ef02f24ac0019","tid":798563,"uid":7015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"內痔嚟<br />\n塞返入去"},{"pid":"301c81ddae1dfb608f217b78a582ed976f15d4a5","tid":798563,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0713dad2bf9be0474ec70d3a3c6ef02f24ac0019","tid":798563,"uid":7015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"內痔嚟<br />\n塞返入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:50:33.000Z","msg":"咁撚大獲？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0152258e0ec8c7ae63a17b1cbdfbb360f816cd60","tid":798563,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b30ba3047d7ab88c8a8a10aabe7346583d6ba242","tid":798563,"uid":27743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:43:07.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:51:20.000Z","msg":"真人真事"},{"pid":"6c39e2115ce32ad25d7146b5279cea75d0e21e41","tid":798563,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0713dad2bf9be0474ec70d3a3c6ef02f24ac0019","tid":798563,"uid":7015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"內痔嚟<br />\n塞返入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:51:50.000Z","msg":"正解,佢好古惑,成日彈出彈入"},{"pid":"2c24051b05ea0b096b903b2afe3a16f7ba270950","tid":798563,"uid":41759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:54:41.000Z","msg":"其實都ok<br />\n<br />\n不過未至於值一塊正皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf29c795efde97407a378997a0714212ae74e5c","tid":798563,"uid":36690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:56:10.000Z","msg":"屙到脫肛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb5a786a7fd0e18686777d343a899dd2fecbf63","tid":798563,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbf29c795efde97407a378997a0714212ae74e5c","tid":798563,"uid":36690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:56:10.000Z","msg":"屙到脫肛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}